This is Sunrise Media ERP — a full-stack Express + React + TypeScript application.

Stack:
- Frontend: React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, TanStack Query, wouter
- Backend: Express (tsx), Drizzle ORM, PostgreSQL via @neondatabase/serverless
- Auth: JWT + bcryptjs

Start command: npm run dev
Dev server: http://localhost:5000

Environment variables required (.env):
  DATABASE_URL=   # PostgreSQL connection string (Supabase pooler URL recommended)
  JWT_SECRET=     # At least 32 random characters

Do NOT change estimate/invoice/payment/WCC logic or database schema without explicit instruction.
